<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>库存明细 - 财务中台</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        primary: '#003eb3',
                        secondary: '#e6f0ff',
                        accent: '#ff6b6b',
                        neutral: '#f5f7fa',
                    },
                    borderRadius: {
                        'sm': '4px',
                        'md': '8px',
                        'lg': '12px',
                        'xl': '16px',
                    },
                },
            }
        }
    </script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="common/styles.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-neutral">
    <div class="flex h-screen">
        <div id="sidebar-container"></div>
        <main class="flex-1 ml-64 p-6 transition-all duration-300 overflow-y-auto" id="main-content">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6">
                    <h1 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">库存明细</h1>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6">
                    <div class="req-marker relative block mb-6" id="req-marker-17">
                        <span class="req-badge" data-req="17"
                              data-title="库存明细Tab导航"
                              data-content='<div class="req-section-title">库存明细Tab导航</div><div class="req-section-title">功能说明</div><ul><li>展示软装合同在金蝶、业务系统、EBS的库存明细</li><li>支持三个来源系统的数据切换查看</li></ul><div class="req-section-title">包含Tab</div><ul><li><strong>金蝶</strong>：金蝶系统库存数据</li><li><strong>业务系统</strong>：svi/积木云装系统数据</li><li><strong>EBS</strong>：EBS系统库存数据</li></ul>'>17</span>
                        <nav class="flex space-x-8 border-b border-gray-200">
                            <button id="tab-kingdee" class="py-3 px-1 border-b-2 border-primary text-primary font-medium">金蝶</button>
                            <button id="tab-business" class="py-3 px-1 border-b-2 border-transparent text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">业务系统</button>
                            <button id="tab-ebs" class="py-3 px-1 border-b-2 border-transparent text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">EBS</button>
                        </nav>
                    </div>

                    <div id="content-kingdee" class="tab-content">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6 flex-nowrap">
                            <div class="req-marker inline-block flex items-center space-x-2 flex-1" id="req-marker-18">
                                <span class="req-badge" data-req="18"
                                      data-title="金蝶筛选条件"
                                      data-content='<div class="req-section-title">金蝶Tab筛选条件</div><div class="req-section-title">基础筛选字段</div><ul><li><strong>财务主体</strong>：下拉选择</li><li><strong>合同号</strong>：文本输入</li><li><strong>物料编码</strong>：文本输入</li><li><strong>单据类型</strong>：下拉选择</li><li><strong>会计期间</strong>：下拉选择（如2026-04）</li></ul><div class="req-section-title">高级筛选</div><p>点击"高级筛选"展开完整筛选表单，支持多条件组合查询</p><em>业务规则：支持按筛选条件导出数据</em>'>18</span>
                                <select id="filter-field-kingdee" class="px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
                                    <option value="entity">财务主体</option>
                                    <option value="contract">合同号</option>
                                    <option value="material">物料编码</option>
                                    <option value="docType">单据类型</option>
                                    <option value="period">会计期间</option>
                                </select>
                                <input type="text" id="filter-value-kingdee" placeholder="按财务主体搜索" class="w-64 px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
                                <button class="px-3 py-2 bg-gray-100 border border-gray-300 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors">
                                    <i data-lucide="search" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                                </button>
                                <button class="px-3 py-2 bg-gray-100 border border-gray-300 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors">
                                    <i data-lucide="refresh-ccw" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                                </button>
                                <button id="advanced-filter-btn-kingdee" class="px-3 py-2 text-primary hover:bg-secondary rounded-md transition-colors flex items-center">
                                    高级筛选
                                    <i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-4 h-4 ml-1"></i>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                            <div class="req-marker inline-block" id="req-marker-19">
                                <span class="req-badge" data-req="19"
                                      data-title="金蝶导出按钮"
                                      data-content='<div class="req-section-title">金蝶导出功能</div><div class="req-section-title">按钮操作</div><ul><li><strong>导出</strong>：支持根据当前筛选条件导出数据</li></ul><div class="req-section-title">导出格式</div><p><em>xlsx格式</em></p><div class="req-section-title">业务规则</div><blockquote>导出的数据范围与筛选条件一致</blockquote>'>19</span>
                                <button id="export-kingdee" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-white rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 flex items-center">
                                    <i data-lucide="download" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2"></i>
                                    导出
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div id="advanced-filter-kingdee" class="hidden bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-md border border-gray-200 mb-6">
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">财务主体</label>
                                    <select class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
                                        <option value="">全部</option>
                                        <option value="org1">财务主体1</option>
                                        <option value="org2">财务主体2</option>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">合同号</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">物料编码</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">单据类型</label>
                                    <select class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
                                        <option value="">全部</option>
                                        <option value="purchaseIn">采购入库单</option>
                                        <option value="purchaseOut">采购退货单</option>
                                        <option value="transfer">直接调拨单</option>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">会计期间</label>
                                    <select class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
                                        <option value="">全部</option>
                                        <option value="2026-04">2026-04</option>
                                        <option value="2026-03">2026-03</option>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mt-4 flex justify-end space-x-2">
                                <button class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
                                    重置
                                </button>
                                <button class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-white rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
                                    查询
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="req-marker relative block" id="req-marker-20">
                            <span class="req-badge" data-req="20"
                                  data-title="金蝶库存明细列表"
                                  data-content='<div class="req-section-title">金蝶Tab列表展示</div><div class="req-section-title">字段清单（20个）</div><ul><li>财务主体、会计期间、合同号</li><li>财务确认竣工日期、业务日期</li><li>单据编号</li><li>单据类型：<em>采购入库单/采购退货单/直接调拨单</em></li><li>物料编码、物料名称、批号</li><li>仓库、仓位</li><li>数量、库存单位</li><li>客户价、项目经理价</li><li>对账单号</li><li>对账状态：<span class="status-dot status-gray"></span>未对账/<span class="status-dot status-orange"></span>待对账/<span class="status-dot status-green"></span>对账成功/<span class="status-dot status-red"></span>对账失败</li><li>来源系统：金蝶</li><li>销售出库单号：<em>出库后反写出库单号</em></li><li>创建时间、修改时间</li></ul><div class="req-section-title">业务规则</div><blockquote>数据来源为金蝶系统，展示完整的库存流转信息</blockquote>'>20</span>
                            <div class="table-wrapper overflow-x-auto">
                                <table class="min-w-full bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
                                <thead class="bg-gray-50">
                                    <tr>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">财务主体</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">会计期间</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">合同号</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">财务确认竣工日期</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">业务日期</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">单据编号</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">单据类型</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">物料编码</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">物料名称</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">批号</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">仓库</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">仓位</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">数量</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">库存单位</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">客户价</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">项目经理价</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">对账单号</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">对账状态</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">来源系统</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">销售出库单号</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">创建时间</th>
                                        <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase">修改时间</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">财务主体1</td>
                                        <td class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">2026-04</td>
                                        <td class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">HT202603001</td>
                                        <td class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">2026-04-10</td>
                                        <td class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">2026-04-08</td>
