                            </table>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-between">
                            <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                                显示 1-2 条，共 2 条
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex space-x-1">
                                <button class="px-3 py-1 border border-gray-300 rounded-md text-sm text-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-50 disabled:opacity-50" disabled>上一页</button>
                                <button class="px-3 py-1 border border-primary bg-primary text-white rounded-md text-sm">1</button>
                                <button class="px-3 py-1 border border-gray-300 rounded-md text-sm text-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-50 disabled:opacity-50" disabled>下一页</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div id="content-business" class="tab-content hidden">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6 flex-nowrap">
                            <div class="req-marker inline-block flex items-center space-x-2 flex-1" id="req-marker-21">
                                <span class="req-badge" data-req="21"
                                      data-title="业务系统筛选条件"
                                      data-content='<div class="req-section-title">业务系统Tab筛选条件</div><div class="req-section-title">基础筛选字段</div><ul><li><strong>财务主体</strong>：下拉选择</li><li><strong>合同号</strong>：文本输入</li><li><strong>物料编码</strong>：文本输入</li><li><strong>单据类型</strong>：下拉选择</li><li><strong>库存截止日期</strong>：日期选择</li></ul><div class="req-section-title">高级筛选</div><p>点击"高级筛选"展开完整筛选表单，支持多条件组合查询</p>'>21</span>
                                <select id="filter-field-business" class="px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
                                    <option value="entity">财务主体</option>
